{"137354":{"detail":{"date":"2000-01-26","platform":"其他","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/11/64/137354_qs82q.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/11/64/137354_qs82q.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/11/64/137354_qs82q.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/11/64/137354_qs82q.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/11/64/137354_qs82q.jpg"},"summary":"　　夜幕低垂，万籁俱静，六段穿梭时空的故事，古老而华丽的剧场，带领我们走进妙不可言的梦境里。 \r\n　　这是一部独具特色的剪影动画，三个主创人物——老人、男孩和女孩聚在一个古老的剧场内，利用他们丰富的想象力以及一台神奇的制衣机器，一边设计服装、撰写剧情，一边创造角色、自行演绎，一则则别具一格的“王子与公主”寓言故事就此诞生。他们创作了六则故事，分别为《钻石公主》、《无花果少年》、《女巫城堡》、《老太太的外衣》、《残酷女王与法布鹭训练师》以及《王子与公主》。故事背景设定在不同时空里，从中世纪到公元三千年，从古埃及到古代日本，延续了古老寓言的同时又颠覆传统。 \r\n　　本动画为芝加哥国际儿童影展最佳动画影片。","name":"Princes et princesses","name_cn":"王子与公主","tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"法国","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MichelOcelot","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童话","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剪影","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"定格动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧洲","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Michel.Ocelot","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短篇集","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"米歇尔·欧斯洛","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小故事","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"其他","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"无","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"200X","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"子供向","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"非日本動畫電影","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"儿童文学","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"7+","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电影","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"7(+2)","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"王子与公主"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"Princes and Princesses"}]},